subject: Olympic Games
Boxing
Olympic Games (2012)
lead_paragraph: Quanitta Underwood won her third straight bout at the United States Olympic boxing trials, winning the 132-pound winners’ bracket with a 25-24 decision over N’yteeyah Sherman.
